PageOverlap Property

CDXML Name:PageOverlap
CDX Constant Name:kCDXProp_PageOverlap
CDX Constant Value:0x0814
Data Size:CDXCoordinate
Property of objects:kCDXObj_Page
First written/read in:ChemDraw 6.0
Required?No

Description:

The amount of overlap of pages when a poster is tiled.

This property is meaningful only for documents with a DrawingSpaceType of type Poster.

If this property is absent:

The pages do not overlap.
